headline.print_headline: Suicide Bomber Kills 13 in Northeastern Nigeria
headline.main: Suicide Bomber Kills 13 in Northeastern Nigeria

lead_paragraph: A female suicide bomber set off an explosion in northeastern Nigeria on Sunday killing 13 people and injuring 65, police said.
